---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout>
  <section class="shell hero">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Liquid Glass publication system</div>
      <h1>Posts, projects, and notes in a glass-native interface.</h1>
      <p class="lead">A static publishing space with soft depth, translucent surfaces, calm motion, and a consistent Apple-style glass material across every page.</p>
    </div>
    <aside class="panel">
      <strong>Publishing workflow</strong>
      <p>Write posts, publish projects, and keep everything fast on GitHub Pages.</p>
      <a class="button" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}posts/`}>Read posts</a>
    </aside>
  </section>
  <section class="shell section">
    <div class="section-head"><h2>Latest posts</h2><a class="tag" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}posts/`}>All posts</a></div>
    <div class="grid posts">
      <a class="card" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}posts/liquid-glass-notes/`}><div class="cover"></div><div class="meta"><span>May 22, 2026</span><span>·</span><span>2 min read</span></div><h3>Liquid Glass Notes</h3><p>A placeholder post exploring translucent interfaces, depth, motion, and modern publishing surfaces.</p><div class="meta"><span class="tag">Design</span><span class="tag">Liquid Glass</span></div></a>
      <a class="card" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}posts/field-notes-from-a-digital-garden/`}><div class="cover"></div><div class="meta"><span>May 21, 2026</span><span>·</span><span>2 min read</span></div><h3>Field Notes from a Digital Garden</h3><p>A placeholder post about collecting small ideas and turning them into a living knowledge system.</p><div class="meta"><span class="tag">Writing</span><span class="tag">Publishing</span></div></a>
      <a class="card" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}posts/quiet-systems-loud-interfaces/`}><div class="cover"></div><div class="meta"><span>May 20, 2026</span><span>·</span><span>2 min read</span></div><h3>Quiet Systems, Loud Interfaces</h3><p>A placeholder post about designing systems that stay calm while the interface remains memorable.</p><div class="meta"><span class="tag">Systems</span><span class="tag">Interface</span></div></a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="shell section">
    <div class="section-head"><h2>Project spotlight</h2><a class="tag" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}projects/`}>Projects</a></div>
    <a class="card" href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}projects/personal-publishing-platform/`}><div class="cover"></div><div class="meta"><span>active</span></div><h3>Personal Publishing Platform</h3><p>A static Astro publication platform for posts, projects, search, RSS, and GitHub Pages deployment.</p></a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
